(58, 0, 'Fun Pictures', 'This is a category for any and all fun pictures', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">This is the place where you will be able to share any and all pictures that you want to share with the teen community. &nbsp;It can be pictures of a beautiful sunrise or sunset. &nbsp;It can be beautiful outdoor scenery pictures. &nbsp;It can be a picture of your favorite car or your favorite house. &nbsp;It can be a picture of you town. &nbsp;It can be a picture of you, your friends, or your family. &nbsp;If it''s of interest to you, there''s bound to be others that share your same interests, so feel free to share any pictures you want to share.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">To have your pictures shared here, please email us your picture(s), and let us know if we can use your name when giving credit for the picture(s). &nbsp;<a href="mailto:content@thesuperteens.com?subject=Submission%20for%20Fun%20Pictures">Email your pictures to: content@thesuperteens.com.</a></span></span></p>', 'blog_13336697434f7e2f6f14a0a.jpg', '2012-04-05 05:37:00', 'Active', 'home', 10),
