(60, 0, 'The Never Ending Story', 'This category will be for all of us to take this story where ever we want.', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: larger;">The Never Ending Story is a place for all of us to let our imaginations take us where ever we want to go. &nbsp;In this category, one of our editorial staff will start a story, then it will be up to all of our registered users to &quot;tell the rest of the story&quot; one piece at a time by adding comments to the story.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: larger;">The only limitations we have, are the limitations we place on our own imaginations. &nbsp;Have fun and unleash the creativity hidden inside each of us.</span></span></p>', 'blog_13336779954f7e4fab76c75.jpg', '2012-04-05 08:07:48', 'Inactive', 'home', 12),
(61, 8, 'Bagel Thin Topped With Peanut Butter And Fruit', 'A super easy and delicious breakfast and it''s also good for you!', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: larger;"><span style="text-align: left; line-height: 16px;">Strawberries contain a phytochemical that may increase the production of leptin, a hunger-suppressing hormone, and adiponectin, a hormone that accelerates fat burning and may fight diabetes. Thank you to womenshealthmag.com for sharing this recipe.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img width="0" height="0" alt="" src="/userfiles/image/flat%20belly%20breakfast1S%20(1).jpg" /><img width="155" height="150" alt="" src="/userfiles/image/flat%20belly%20breakfast1S%20(1).jpg" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: larger;"><span style="text-align: left;">1 Thomas'' 100% Whole Wheat Bagel Thin</span><br style="text-align: left; font-size: 12px;" />\r\n<span style="text-align: left;">2 Tbsp natural peanut butter</span><br style="text-align: left; font-size: 12px;" />\r\n<span style="text-align: left;">1 medium banana, sliced</span><br style="text-align: left; font-size: 12px;" />\r\n<span style="text-align: left;">4 strawberries, sliced*</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: larger;"><span style="text-align: left;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Our health and nutrition section offers nutritional and exercise tips for a healthy lifestyle.  Healthy recipes and exercise tips will be the order of the day in this section.  To submit your recipes, exercise tips and regimens, please email them to us at: <a href="mailto:content@thesuperteens.com?subject=Suggestions%20for%20Health%20and%20Nutrition">content@thesuperteens.com</a><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'blog_13336834684f7e650cb0a0d.jpg', '2012-04-05 09:39:01', 'Active', 'home', 0),
