(68, 58, 'Scenes from Hawaii', 'Some beautiful pictures from Hawaii submitted by Annie', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">Here are some beautiful pictures from Annie''s trip to Hawaii last year. &nbsp;Enjoy.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/Hawaiian_Flower1.jpg" width="400" height="244" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/Sea_Life1.jpg" width="373" height="250" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/Sea_Life2.jpg" width="392" height="250" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/Sea_Life3.jpg" width="400" height="249" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/Water1.jpg" width="400" height="250" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">&nbsp;<span style="line-height: 12pt; ">This is the place where you will be able to share any and all pictures that you want to share with the teen community. &nbsp;It can be pictures of a beautiful sunrise or sunset. &nbsp;It can be beautiful outdoor scenery pictures. &nbsp;It can be a picture of your favorite car or your favorite house. &nbsp;It can be a picture of you town. &nbsp;It can be a picture of you, your friends, or your family. &nbsp;If it''s of interest to you, there''s bound to be others that share your same interests, so feel free to share any pictures you want to share.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; ">To have your pictures shared here, please email us your picture(s), and let us know if we can use your name when giving credit for the picture(s). &nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:content@thesuperteens.com?subject=Submission%20for%20Fun%20Pictures" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; ">Email your pictures to: content@thesuperteens.com.</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'blog_13338931194f8197ff0b230.jpg', '2012-04-07 19:53:17', 'Active', 'home', 0),
(69, 1, 'Kearns High School and Operation Kids Robot', 'Kearns High School in Kearns Utah put together a wonderful service project for students at the Primary Children''s Hospital in Salt Lake City', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">A group of High School students from Kearns High School in Kearns Utah, put together a great service project to raise the funds necessary to put a robot into the Primary Children''s Hospital in Salt Lake City Utah. &nbsp;This robot is designed to help students continue with their education while spending extended periods of time at Primary Children''s Hospital for treatment of serious, life threatening illnesses. &nbsp;A big hats off to all of the students and faculty that were able to make this valuable service available to patients at Primary Children''s Hospital. &nbsp;This video is from icougars on Youtube.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/kDxTXnkmcKU" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; "><b style="line-height: 12pt; "><span style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white; ">Now it&rsquo;s your turn to be recognized for making a difference. We are looking for the pictures, videos, and stories of you and your friends doing things that make a difference in the lives of others.</span></b></span></span></p>\r\n<p><b style="line-height: 12pt; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">To send us your pictures, videos and articles on The Super Teens in action, please click on the following link and email them to us: <a