(72, 2, 'Where Was This Picture Taken', 'We want your guesses as to where this picture was taken.', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">One of our users, Annie, submitted this picture from one of her trips. &nbsp;Where was this picture taken?</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">No on correctly guessed that this picture is of the old prison Alcatraz, located in the harbor outside of San Francisco.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/Where3.jpg" width="387" height="250" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 12pt; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; ">Guessing where this picture was taken will be one of the fun things you get to do on this site. &nbsp;Everyone that correctly guesses where this picture was taken will be entered into a drawing for a free Super Teens t-shirt. &nbsp;To register your guess, send us an email to:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@thesuperteens.com?subject=Guess%20for%20the%20location%20of%20Adventure1%20in%20Where%20Are%20The%20Super%20Teens"><span style="color:blue">info@thesuperteens.com</span></a>&nbsp;and tell us your guess for picture Where3.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 12pt; "><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 12pt; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">This category is a fun way to show off where any of The Super Teens have traveled and will be a fun way to highlight beautiful scenery, settings, and historical sites. &nbsp;We want pictures showing you and your friends in scenic loca