(85, 2, 'We want your guesses as to where this picture was taken', 'Where was this picture taken?', '<p>Submitted by our user VT1, where was this picture taken?</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for all of your guesses as to where this picture was taken. &nbsp;We had several of our users guess that this photo was taken at Buckingham Palace, in Great Britain. &nbsp;Out of the winners, Annie1 was drawn as the winner of one of The Super Teens t-shirts.</p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/Where4.jpg" width="394" height="250" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Guessing where this picture was taken will be one of the fun things you get to do on this site.  Everyone that correctly guesses where this picture was taken will be entered into a drawing for a free Super Teens t-shirt.  </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">To register your guess, send us an email to:<a href="mailto:info@thesuperteens.com?subject=Where%20Picture%20Where4%20was%20taken"> <span style="color: blue;">info@thesuperteens.com</span></a> and tell us your guess for picture Where4.</span></p>', 'blog_13345801684f8c13c8b0586.jpg', '2012-04-15 18:44:24', 'Active', 'home', 0),
