(92, 1, 'Barren County High School Beta Club Valentine Project', 'A great service project making an delivering Valentines to the local nursing home', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">The Beta Club from Barren County High School in South Central Kentucky, does an annual service project where they make Valentine''s Day cards for the residents of a local nursing home and then personally deliver them.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/-DsZzNaZeKw" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><b><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">Now it&rsquo;s your turn to be recognized for making a difference. We are looking for the pictures, videos, and stories of you and your friends doing things that make a difference in the lives of others.</span></b></p>\r\n<p><b style="line-height: 12pt; "><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; ">To send us your pictures, videos and articles on The Super Teens in action, please click on the following link and email them to us:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:content@thesuperteens.com?subject=Submission%20for%20The%20Super%20Teens%20In%20Acation"><span style="color:blue">Content@thesuperteens.com</span></a></span></b></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 12pt; "><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'blog_13348389354f900697118e6.jpg', '2012-04-18 18:37:18', '