(93, 5, 'Amazing Violinist Plays "Firework"', 'This guy is amazing! You have to check him out!!', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: larger;">On his Youtube page Violin4Real shares his amazing talent. He plays by ear! I love the way he puts it all together.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><iframe width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/TzySasqMCfc" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: larger;"><span style="line-height: 12pt;">The Arts, is a showcase for the artistry of teens in all formats. This is the platform where all artists will be able to have their work shown in the public spotlight. We want your music videos, dance videos, paintings, sculptures, photographs, and all other forms of non-commercially produced artistry. This is your opportunity to shine and show the world your work in art.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: larger;"><span style="line-height: 12pt; background-color: white;">To submit your videos, photographs, and other works of art, please click on the link and send them to us via email: </span></span></span><span style="line-height: 12pt; background-color: white;"><font color="#0000ff" size="4"><a href="mailto:content@thesuperteens.com?subject=Submission%20for%20the%20Arts"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: larger;">Content@thesuperteens.com</span></span></a></font></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'blog_13348522614f903aa529484.jpg', '2012-04-18 22:19:23', 'Active', 'home', 0),
(94, 6, 'How To Do A Smokey Eye', 'Great tips on how to get that perfect smokey eye look.', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: larger;">Thanks to VivaGlamLana on her Youtube page&nbsp;for sharing her tips for getting that perfect&nbsp; smokey eye.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><iframe width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/fqR6zpggejc" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: larger;"><span style="font-size: larger;"><span style="line-height: 12pt; background-color: white;"><a href="mailto:content@thesuperteens.com?subject=Beauty%20and%20Fashion%20Tips"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: larger;">To send us your pictures, videos and articles on fashion and beauty, please click on this link and send us an email:</span></span></a></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'blog_13348552364f904644ec476.jpg', '2012-04-18 23:08:59', 'Active', 'home', 0),
(95, 0, 'Today Is The First Day Of The Rest Of Our Lives', 'It''s true. Today really is the first day of the rest of our lives', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">We''ve all heard the saying, &quot;Today is the first day of the rest of our lives.&quot; It''s true. Today really can be the first day of the rest of our lives. It doesn''t matter what we''ve done in life. &nbsp;It doesn''t matter if we haven''t always tried to do our best. &nbsp;It doesn''t matter if there are a lot of people out there who say there''s no way we will ever amount to anything. &nbsp;It doesn''t matter if we''ve made some pretty major mistakes in our lives.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">What does matter is what we do with today. &nbsp;If we want to achieve great success in life and make all our dreams come true, we just have to remember to think good thoughts and then decide to act on those thoughts. Each and every one of us have been given unique talents and abilities, so our success will be unique to us. &nbsp;We don''t have to measure our success based on the criteria of someone else. &nbsp;It''s up to us to determine what success is, and then work to achieve it</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">Over the next few weeks, I will be using this blog to work and inspire others to grow, to mature, and to achieve their full potential. &nbsp;If I have learned anything in life, it''s that true success can only come when you help others to get what they want in life. &nbsp;By helping others, we help ourselves.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">Might we all realize that today is the first day of the rest of our lives, and today, we will work to make a difference.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">KR</span></span></p>\r\n<p>.</p>', 'blog_13348848014f90b9c1c3709.jpg', '2012-04-19 07:21:46', 'Active', 'blog', 0),
(96, 7, 'Game Winning Basketball Shot', 'This game winning shot is just awesome.', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">This game winning basketball shot is amazing. &nbsp;The team is down 1 point, and there are 0.6 seconds left on the clock. &nbsp;You''ve got to see it to believe it.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/B3_1ehifUBU" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>\r\n<p><span style="background-color: white; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 12pt; ">This category is designed to highlight teen involvement in all kinds of sports. &nbsp;We want your photos, videos, and articles hightlighting teen participation in any kind of sporting events and endeavors.</span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 12pt; "><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; "><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white; ">To send us your pictures, videos and articles on teen sports, please email them to us:&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 12pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; "><a href="mailto:content@thesuperteens.com?subject=Sports%20Submission"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;background:white">content@thesuperteens.com</span></a></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 12pt; "><span style="font-size: 10pt; "><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'blog_13349220334f914b31755e6.jpg', '2012-04-19 17:42:19', 'Active', 'home', 0),
(98, 1, 'Watertown High School Robotics Club Service Project', 'A great service project to help a little boy walk better', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">&nbsp;The Watertown High School Robotics Club did this community service project to help a little boy with extreme walking challenges. &nbsp;A very commendable project to benefit this cute little boy.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/couvC9lHM3E" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>\r\n<p><b style="line-height: normal; "><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white">Now it&rsquo;s your turn to be recognized for making a difference. We are looking for the pictures, videos, and stories of you and your friends doing things that make a difference in the lives of others.</span></b></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><b style="line-height: normal; "><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white">To send us your pictures, videos and articles on The Super Teens in action, please click on the following link and email them to us:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:content@thesuperteens.com?subject=Submission%20for%20The%20Super%20Teens%20In%20Acation"><span style="color:blue">Content@thesuperteens.com</span></a></span></b></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-heig