(99, 7, 'Jordan Yamoah Setting High School Pole Vault Record', 'Watch as Jordan Yamoah sets a New York State High School pole vault record', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">Joran Yamoah from Arlington High School sets a New York State high school pole vault record with a vault of 17'' 1&quot;.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/IbMuGIFK7hs" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0"><br></iframe></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">This category is designed to highlight teen involvement in all kinds of sporting activities. &nbsp;We want your photos, videos, and articles highlighting teen participation in any kind of sporting events and endeavors.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">To send us your pictures, videos, and articles on teen sports, please email them to us at: <a href="mailto:content@thesuperteens.com?subject=Sports%20submission">content@thesuperteens.com</a></span></span></p>', 'blog_13350455264f932d96a26fb.jpg', '2012-04-21 04:00:35', 'Active', 'home', 0),
(100, 0, 'The Principle of Service', 'Today''s blog entry is on the principle of service', '<p>Today I would like to address the principle of service. &nbsp;Service is a law of nature. &nbsp;A law of nature is a law that can''t be changed. &nbsp;A good example of a law of nature would be the law of gravity. &nbsp;If you stand on top of a very tall building and you drop a rock, that rock will always fall down. &nbsp;It will never fall up, because of the law of gravity.</p>\r\n<p>How many of us would like to get more out of life? &nbsp;I don''t know of many people that would tell you that they have all they need in life. &nbsp;Instead, most people would jump at the chance to get more out of life. This is where service comes in to play.</p>\r\n<p>Service is another law of nature. &nbsp;If you provide service to someone else, you will always be rewarded in return. &nbsp;Your reward may not come from the person that you provided the service to, but just like any other law of nature, you have to be rewarded. &nbsp;If you want more out of life all you have to do is increase the quantity and quality of service that you provide for others, and you will achieve the success you desire.</p>\r\n<p>So if you want more out of life, if you want to be happier in life, if you want to find great joy in life, then just look around you and find the opportunities to serve others. &nbsp;I can guarantee you that the joy you feel in life will be greatly compounded. &nbsp;Serve joyfully. &nbsp;Serve gratefully. Serve with an open heart and you will be rewarded with untold riches.</p>\r\n<p>KR</p>', 'blog_13350475324f93356c1ec11.jpg', '2012-04-21 04:34:02', 'Active', 'blog', 0),
(101, 2, 'Where was this photo taken', 'This week''s photo should be a pretty easy guess', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">This week''s photo should be pretty familiar to most everyone.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">It must be time to brush up on American History. &nbsp;No one correctly identified this National Monument. &nbsp;This a picture of the Lincoln Memorial.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/Where5.jpg" width="389" height="250" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; ">Guessing where this picture was taken will be one of the fun things you get to do on this site. Everyone that correctly guesses where this picture was taken will be entered into a drawing for a free Super Teens t-shirt.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; ">To register your guess, send us an email to:<a href="mailto:info@thesuperteens.com?subject=Where%20Picture%20Where5%20was%20taken"><span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>info@thesuperteens.com</a><span class="apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>and tell us your guess for picture Where5.</span></p>', 'blog_13351795104f9538f6cf1ba.jpg', '2012-04-22 17:13:43', 'Active', 'home', 0),
(102, 58, 'Fisherman''s Wharf In San Francisco', 'Fun pictures from Fisherman''s Wharf in San Francisco', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">Our user Annie1 sent in these pictures from one of her trips to San Francisco, CA.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/SF1.jpg" width="394" height="250" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">The sea lions take over the rafts at one of the piers.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/SF2.jpg" width="400" height="247" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/SF3.jpg" width="400" height="249" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; "><span style="background-color: white; color: black; line-height: 115%; ">This is the place where you will be able to share any and all pictures that you want to share with the teen community. &nbsp;It can be pictures of a beautiful sunrise or sunset. &nbsp;It can be beautiful outdoor scenery pictures. &nbsp;It can be a picture of your favorite car or your favorite house. &nbsp;It can be a picture of your town. &nbsp;It can be a picture of you, your friends, or your family. &nbsp;If it''s of interest to you, there''s bound to be others that share your same interests, so feel free to share any pictures you want to share.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; "><span style="line-height: 115%; ">To have your pictures shared here, please email us your picture(s), and let us know if we can use your name when giving credit for the picture(s).</span><span style="line-height: 115%; ">&nbsp; </span><span style="line-height: 115%; ">Email your pictures to: <a href="mailto:content@thesuperteens.com?subject=Fun%20Pictures%20Submission">content@thesuperteens.com</a></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'blog_13351811124f953f38