(104, 1, 'Lincoln High School Service Project', 'A unique idea for a service project to help feed the homeless', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">This video is of a unique service project called the Empty Bowl Project, was done by the Lincoln High School students in Orem Utah. &nbsp;It was a fund raiser to help feed the homeless.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/MYIf1JlBs5o" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>\r\n<p><b style="line-height: normal; "><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white">Now it&rsquo;s your turn to be recognized for making a difference. We are looking for the pictures, videos, and stories of you and your friends doing things that make a difference in the lives of others.</span></b></p>\r\n<p><b style="line-height: normal; "><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;background:white">To send us your pictures, videos and articles on The Super Teens in action, please click on the following link and email them to us:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:content@thesuperteens.com?subject=Submission%20for%20The%20Super%20Teens%20In%20Acation"><span style="color:blue">Content@thesuperteens.com</span></a></span></b></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; background-image: initia