(122, 58, 'Ocean Shores WA', 'Pictures from my trip to Ocean Shores Washington', '<p><span style="font-family: Arial; "><span style="font-size: larger; ">Submitted by our member Annie1, here are her pictures from her vacation that she took with her family to Ocean Shores Washington.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/Beach2.jpg" width="400" height="249" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/Beach1.jpg" width="376" height="250" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/Beach3.jpg" width="395" height="250" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/Beach4.jpg" width="395" height="250" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/Beach5.jpg" width="400" height="246" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><img src="/userfiles/image/Beach6.jpg" width="400" height="248" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p><span style="background-color: white; color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; ">This is the place where you will be able to share any and all pictures that you want to share with the teen community. &nbsp;It can be pictures of a beautiful sunrise or sunset. &nbsp;It can be beautiful outdoor scenery pictures. &nbsp;It can be a picture of your favorite car or your favorite house. &nbsp;It can be a picture of your town. &nbsp;It can be a picture of you, your friends, or your family. &nbsp;If it''s of interest to you, there''s bound to be others that share your same interests, so feel free to share any pictures you want to share.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; background-color: white; ">To have your pictures shared here, please email us your picture(s), and let us know if we can use your name when giving credit for the picture(s).&nbsp;</span><span class="apple-converted-space" style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; background-color: white; ">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; background-color: white; ">Email your pictures to:</span><span class="apple-converted-space" style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; background-color: white; ">&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:content@thesuperteens.com?subject=Fun%20Pictures%20Submission" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; background-color: white; ">content@thesuperteens.com</a></p>\r\n<p style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; "><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'blog_13360461104fa2721e86ccc.jpg', '2012-05-02 17:57:24', 'Active', 'home', 0),
